# Overview

AMMON: A GREAT SERVAN 
BOOK OF MORMON VIDEOGAMES 

![AMMON](assets/tiles/AMMON.png?raw=true "Title")

This videogame series were created to teach children the stories of the Book of Mormon: Another Testament of Jesus Christ
This game is the story of AMMON a prophet of the Lord. 

MOVE FORWARD: RIGHT ARROW or D
MOVE BACKWARD: LEFT ARROW or a
JUMP: UP ARROW or a

FIRST LEVEL: Collet sheeps for the king


